textutils (2.0-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * New maintainer.
  * Added missing backslashes to tr.1 (closes: #49941).
  * Fixed tsort(1) to treat cycles correctly (closes: #65461, #43610).
  * Added a new option -r which allows cat to display control characters
    without ambiguity (closes: #4335).
  * Implemented new options --separator and --check-fields for uniq
    (closes: #31106).
  * Document that od -ta only uses the lower 7 bits (closes: #66274).
  * Included md5sum as md5sum.textutils (closes: #34234).

 -- Herbert Xu <herbert@debian.org>  Wed, 28 Jun 2000 15:23:34 +1000

